data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome to this beautiful home that effortlessly blends style and functionality! As you enter, you're greeted by the expansive open living room, seamlessly connected to the well-appointed kitchen featuring a breakfast bar and a cozy breakfast nook. The kitchen boasts ample cabinet and countertop space, complemented by a convenient walk-in pantry. The first floor is complete with a formal dining room and a half bathroom, enhancing the home's practicality. Upstairs, discover a spacious game room, providing a versatile space for entertainment and relaxation. The primary bedroom is a retreat with a generous walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom featuring a dual vanity sink, a soaking tub, a standalone shower, and abundant cabinet storage. The upper level also accommodates three additional roomy bedrooms, each equipped with walk-in closets, sharing a full-size bathroom with a single vanity sink and a shower/tub combo. For added convenience, there's a dedicated laundry room upstairs. Step into the fully fenced backyard, where a patio awaits, offering a perfect spot for outdoor gatherings, surrounded by ample green space. Don't miss the chance to call this wonderful property your new home!
